(264, 1, '2018-02-14 23:43:02', '2018-02-14 22:43:02', '{\n    \"mesmerize-child::custom_logo\": {\n        \"value\": 263,\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2018-02-14 22:40:15\"\n    },\n    \"mesmerize-child::page_content\": {\n        \"value\": \"<!--@@CPPAGEID[6]@@--><div  data-label=\\\"About\\\" data-id=\\\"about-1\\\" data-export-id=\\\"about-1\\\" data-category=\\\"about\\\" class=\\\"about-1 content-section content-section-spacing\\\" id=\\\"about-1\\\" style=\\\"background-color: #ffffff; background-image: none;\\\">\\n<div  class=\\\"gridContainer\\\">\\n<div  class=\\\"row text-center\\\">\\n<div  class=\\\"section-title-col\\\" data-type=\\\"column\\\">\\n<h2  class=\\\"\\\">\\u00c0 Propos</h2>\\n<p  class=\\\"lead\\\">Elys\\u00e9es Nails Paris, est situe au centre du 8eme arrondissement de Paris \\u00e0 500 m\\u00e8tres du Palais de l\'Elys\\u00e9es et de H\\u00f4tel palace Le Bristol. Et bien sur \\u00e0 deux pas des Champs Elys\\u00e9es, place de Concorde et place saint Augustin. \\n<br ><br >Salon de manucure deco moderne et design hyper tendance, chic et sophistiqu\\u00e9e. Avec 3 postes de Manucures, 2 fauteuils pour la beaut\\u00e9 des pieds et une cabine de soins d\\u00e9di\\u00e9e aux epilations \\u00e0 la cire.&nbsp;</p>\\n\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n<div  class=\\\"row\\\">\\n<div  class=\\\"col-xs bottom-xs flexbox image-group-bottom-3-img space-bottom-xs center-xs\\\"><img  class=\\\"left-img shadow-large-black\\\" data-size=\\\"500x300\\\" src=\\\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/cropped-Merry_Christmas_03-3.png\\\"> <img  class=\\\"center-img shadow-large-black\\\" data-size=\\\"500x300\\\" src=\\\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/cropped-sample_02.jpg\\\"> <img  class=\\\"right-img shadow-large-black\\\" data-size=\\\"500x300\\\" src=\\\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/cropped-215602f2c2944bb252fd882a5bd67e84-chinese-paints.jp