gridContainer\">\n<div  class=\"row text-center\">\n<div  class=\"section-title-col\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h2  class=\"\">Nos Produits</h2>\n<p  class=\"lead\">Nous vous proposons, des soins de manucures hauts de gammes sur mesures pour vous aux meilleurs prix.<br >Avec la gamme de produits OPI nouvelle collection et des équipements de dernière génération.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"row spaced-cols\" data-type=\"row\">\n<div  class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 space-bottom\">\n\n<img  class=\"face\" src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/v2.i1191484.w341.h200.x03746949.png\">\n<div  data-type=\"column\" class=\"col-padding-small col-padding-small-xs description-container\">\n\n\n\n\n<img  class=\"custom-image\" src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/marque-opi-01.jpg\"><a  class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://www.opi.com\" target=\"_blank\" data-cp-link=\"1\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"position: relative; top: 0px; left: 0px;\">Visiter le site</a></div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 space-bottom\">\n\n<img  class=\"face\" src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/v2.i1052846.w197.h40.x4A0A4FF4.png\">\n<div  data-type=\"column\" class=\"col-padding-small col-padding-small-xs description-container\">\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 space-bottom\">\n\n<img  class=\"face\" src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/v2.i1156836.w229.h40.png\">\n<div  data-type=\"column\" class=\"col-padding-small col-padding-small-xs description-container\">\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div  id=\"testimonials-5\" style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" data-label=\"Testimonials\" data-id=\"testimonials-5\" data-export-id=\"testimonials-5\" data-category=\"testimonials\" class=\"testimonials-5 content-section content-section-spacing\">\n<div  class=\"gridContainer\">\n<div  class=\"row\">\n<div  data-type=\"column\" class=\"section-title-col\">\n<h2  class=\"\">Nos Clients</h2>\n<p  class=\"lead\">Nous vous prévilligeons la qualité qui prime sur la quantité, telle est notre devise!</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"row spaced-cols content-center-sm\" data-type=\"row\">\n<div  class=\"col-sm-4\">\n<div  class=\"card y-move bordered\" data-type=\"column\">\n\n<i  class=\"fa icon color1 fa-quote-left small\"></i>\n<p  class=\"text-center\">Super équipe !!! J’ai fait la pose résine et vernis semi permanent la qualité est super et il y a un large choix de couleur,\n\nje recommande à 100%\n\n\n</p>\n<img  src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/cropped-avatar-00-1.png\" class=\"round icon\">\n<h6  class=\"\">Dely Margaux</h6>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm-4\">\n<div  class=\"card y-move bordered\" data-type=\"column\">\n\n<i  class=\"fa icon color1 fa-quote-left small\"></i>\n<p  class=\"text-center\">J’ai apprécié ma visite dans ce salon et je le recommande vivement\nDeco tres soignée ambiance chaleureuse et manucure très bien réalisée</p>\n<img  src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/cropped-avatar-01-2.png\" class=\"round icon\">\n<h6  class=\"\">Lacondemine</h6>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm-4\">\n<div  class=\"card y-move bordered\" data-type=\"column\">\n\n<i  class=\"fa icon color1 fa-quote-left small\"></i>\n<p  class=\"text-center\">Petit salon de quartier très mignon, décoré avec goût, patron et employées adorable. Manucure bien faite, le travail n’est pas fait à la chaine et c’est agréable !&nbsp;&nbsp;Je recommande</p>\n<img  src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/cropped-avatar-02-1.png\" class=\"round icon\">\n<h6  class=\"\">Camille</h6>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div  data-label=\"Features\" data-id=\"features-12\" data-export-id=\"features-12\" data-category=\"features\" class=\"features-12 content-section content-section-spacing \" id=\"features-1\" style=\"background-color: #f5fafd;\">\n<div  class=\"gridContainer\">\n<div  class=\"row text-center\">\n<div  class=\"section-title-col\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h2  class=\"\">Nos Prestations</h2>\n<p  class=\"lead\">Les soins réalisés par des professionnels diplômés qui sont là pour vous faire un agréable moment priviligié de détente.\nL’embellissement de vos ongles et vos mains et pieds avec, une garantie de travail d’excellence pour les rendre impeccable.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"row spaced-cols\" data-type=\"row\">\n<div  class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-6 \">\n<div  class=\"row space-bottom\">\n<div  class=\"col-sm-fit icon-column\"><i  class=\"fa icon color2 fa-mars bordered round\"> </i></div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5  class=\"color2\">BEAUTÉ DES MAINS POUR HOMME</h5>\n<p  class=\"\">Manucure</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">23€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">25m-30m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Beauté des pieds</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">35€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">5m-40m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Beauté des mains + pieds</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">53€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">1h-1h15m</h4>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-6 \">\n<div  class=\"row space-bottom\">\n<div  class=\"col-sm-fit icon-column\"><i  class=\"fa icon color2 fa-delicious bordered round\"> </i></div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5  class=\"color2\">SOIN DES MAINS / HAND CARE</h5>\n<p  class=\"\">Beauté des pieds + vernis OPI</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">27€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">35m-40m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Beauté des mains + semi permanente (dépose)</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">40€/43€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">30m-40m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Pose semi permanente french ou vernis french</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">+5€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\"><span  style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: left;\">10m</span></h4>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-6 \">\n<div  class=\"row space-bottom\">\n<div  class=\"col-sm-fit icon-column\"><i  class=\"fa icon fa-cube round bordered color2\"> </i></div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5  class=\"color2\">SOINS DES PIEDS / FOOT CARE</h5>\n<p  class=\"\">Beauté des pieds + vernis</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">39€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">40m-50m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Beauté des pieds + semi permanente (dépose)</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">55€/58€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">50m-55m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Pose vernis french ou semi permanente french</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">+5€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">15m</h4>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-6 \">\n<div  class=\"row space-bottom\">\n<div  class=\"col-sm-fit icon-column\"><i  class=\"fa icon fa-database round bordered color2\"> </i></div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5  class=\"color2\">POSE SEMI PERMANENTE</h5>\n<p  class=\"\">Pose semi permanente des mains (dépose)</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">30€/33€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">30m-35m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Pose semi permanente des pieds (dépose)</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">35€/38€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">30m-35m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Pose semi permanente french</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">+5€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">15m</h4>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-6 \">\n<div  class=\"row space-bottom\">\n<div  class=\"col-sm-fit icon-column\"><i  class=\"fa icon fa-connectdevelop round bordered color2\"> </i></div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5  class=\"color2\">FORFAIT MAINS ET PIEDS\n\n+ semi permanente</h5>\n<p  class=\"\">Beauté des mains et pieds + vernis/french</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">58€/68€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">1h15m-1h30m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Beauté des mains et pieds + semi permanente (dépose)</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">90€/95€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">1h30m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Beauté des mains et pieds + semi french (dépose)</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">100€/10€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">1h40m</h4>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-6\">\n<div  class=\"row space-bottom\">\n<div  class=\"col-sm-fit icon-column\"><i  class=\"fa icon color2 fa-flash bordered round\"> </i></div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5  class=\"color2\">SERVICE RAPIDE</h5>\n<p  class=\"\">Dépose semi permanente</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">10€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">15m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Dépose les faux ongles</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">15€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">15m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Préparation ongle cassé</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">7€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">10m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Pose de vernis des mains</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">10€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">15m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Pose de vernis des pieds</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">13€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">10m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Pose de vernis sur faux ongles</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">15€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">10m</h4>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-6\">\n<div  class=\"row space-bottom\">\n<div  class=\"col-sm-fit icon-column\"><i  class=\"fa icon color2 fa-plus bordered round\"> </i></div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5  class=\"color2\">SERVICE PLUS</h5>\n<p  class=\"\">Massage des pieds (RDV)</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">25€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">20m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Massage des mains (RDV)</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">20€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">20m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Épilation sourcils (RDV)</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">15€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">15m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Épilation mention (RDV)</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">10€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">10m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Épilation lèvre (RDV)</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">10€</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">10m</h4>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div  id=\"contact-1\" data-label=\"Contact\" data-id=\"contact-1\" data-export-id=\"contact-1\" data-category=\"contact\" class=\"contact-1 content-section content-section-spacing white-text\" data-parallax-depth=\"20\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/Elysees_Nails_FRK_371494_9_xxxxx.jpg&quot;); background-size: cover; background-position: center top;\">\n<div  class=\"gridContainer\">\n<div  class=\"row text-center\">\n<div  class=\"section-title-col\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h2  class=\"\">Contactez-nous</h2>\n<p  class=\"lead\">L’ouverture de l’institut de manucure est ouvert du lundi au samedi de 10h à 20h00 sans interruption avec ou sans rendez vous.<br >Ouvert les jours férié et dimanche sur RDV.<br >Métro : Miromesnil ou St Augustin ligne 9 et 13 <br >Bus : ligne 22, 28, 43, 80, 84, 94&nbsp;</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"row text-center\">\n<div  class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2 contact-form-wrapper inline-info\">\n<div  class=\"card large-padding\">\n<div  class=\"\" data-content-shortcode=\"mesmerize_contact_form shortcode=&quot;put_wpgm id=1&quot;\" data-editable=\"true\">[mesmerize_contact_form shortcode=\"put_wpgm id=1\"]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Accueil', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-18 19:39:59', '2018-02-18 18:39:59', '', 6, 'https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/6-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
